16. Nandikkhayavagga Jīvakambavanasamādhisutta ^n160 Ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā rājagahe viharati jīvakambavane. 
Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: 
“bhikkhavo”ti …pe… 
“samādhiṁ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha. 
