Tatiyaṁ. 
1. Jambukhādakavagga Kimatthiyasutta ^n317 “Kimatthiyaṁ, āvuso sāriputta, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṁ vussatī”ti? 
“Dukkhassa kho, āvuso, pariññatthaṁ bhagavati brahmacariyaṁ vussatī”ti. 
