1. Jambukhādakavagga Dukkarapañhāsutta ^n329 “Kiṁ nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, imasmiṁ dhammavinaye dukkara”nti? 
“Pabbajjā kho, āvuso, imasmiṁ dhammavinaye dukkarā”ti. 
“Pabbajitena panāvuso, kiṁ dukkara”nti? 
“Pabbajitena kho, āvuso, abhirati dukkarā”ti. 
“Abhiratena panāvuso, kiṁ dukkara”nti? 
